body:
Input:
```mlir
firrtl.circuit "Foo"  {
  firrtl.module @Foo() {
    %invalid_ui0 = firrtl.invalidvalue : !firrtl.uint<0>
  }
}
```
Output of `circt-opt -lower-firrtl-to-hw` contains `firrtl.invalidvalue` for some reason.
```
  hw.module @Foo() {
    %invalid_ui0 = firrtl.invalidvalue : !firrtl.uint<0>
    hw.output
  }
```
